Race through a collapsing city in a game that helped launch the infinite runner genre. From its gorgeous music to its searing imageryexploding windows, falling buildingsCanabalt overflows with style and atmosphere. Surviving even a single minute requires split-second reflexes and a whole lot of luck. Plus, after years of updatesincluding all-new modes like shared-screen multiplayerthis already epic game has been polished to perfection.
